{"tid":2340284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線「極深黃良心記者」 被撐警藍絲圍毆 稱拳腳來自四面八方","createTime":"2020-12-25T10:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T12:29:27.000Z","uid":25240,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"82bd8c6f22a6304e83fed530b1613649744d74c5","tid":2340284,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T10:28:21.000Z","msg":"個個就係係cctvb 真理部既冼志<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係支那讀ug 然後入新華社返工 再轉入cctvb <br />\n睇埋個姓都200% 肯定係港漂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MrbBPZ0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMrbBPZ0.png&h=9520bec7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>TVB新聞部3人採訪隊，前往拍攝由「藍絲帶運動」、「撐警大聯盟」及「正義聯盟」三個團體主辦的反佔中撐警察集會時，慘遭集會人士圍毆，送往伊利沙伯醫院治理。集會者大罵記者是「漢奸」、「走狗」。無綫電視新聞部嚴厲譴責這次襲擊事件。<br />\n其中攝影師雷釗河憶述經過時表示，自己最先被打。他說，當時有一名大叔見到他的攝影機上有TVB的標誌，然後就拉扯攝影機的背帶，將攝影機扯跌地上，但無表明動機。雷說，他當時向大叔說：「喂！這樣我要報警！」大叔隨即退走，但雷將他捉住，重申要報警，旁邊的撐警集會人士便開始起哄，期間有人向雷推撞，為數多達10多人。<br />\n<br />\n另一名TVB攝影師潘國輝說，當時他正在拍攝集會畫面，看到同事雷釗河被包圍襲擊，被勒住頸部，於是拿起攝影機上前，並想辦法帶雷離開。潘說，當時一手拿著攝影機，一手抱著雷，打算解救他離開現場，豈料，沿途兩人都被拳打腳踢襲擊。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">TVB記者冼志則說，當時見到有同事受傷，衣服被扯爛，於是與潘一前一後保護雷，豈料三人都被攻擊，拳打腳踢。冼形容，拳腳襲擊來自四面八方，他還被人拉扯領呔。</span><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rZnWbSJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZnWbSJ.png&h=a6819a13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/azMLIFiABmI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FazMLIFiABmI&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=e37b2b72\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/azMLIFiABmI</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n認真想問下呢個世界有咩工好做過cctvb 真理部<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n背景唔紅到黑既 袁花一律唔請 （eg. 章詠欣 / 鄭康煥）<br />\n入到去大安旨意作fake news 抹黑之餘<br />\n仲有一大堆左膠幫手兜「內部抗爭 對抗袁志偉」/ 「打份工被迫」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連新華社出身都可以吹到「深黃良心」 <br />\n我諗遲d 維尼都變手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42cd393a34168b7042f6f1c9a740c1682d608f70","tid":2340284,"uid":25240,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T10:31:02.000Z","msg":"打漏左： 「tvb良知記者內部反抗 」 一詞出自於Johnson Chu <br />\n舊年第一時間衝出黎幫cctvb 真理部護航<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家唔知潛撚左去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJohnson Chu <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/johnsonchu728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fjohnsonchu728&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQFNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=2a93536d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/johnsonchu728</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bBOMG2S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbBOMG2S.png&h=6062af63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88AfAnR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88AfAnR.png&h=0cabbdf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QyCu9cJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQyCu9cJ.png&h=2e9bb146&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e789554686528dff620cdd6031ef5a3fc576c705","tid":2340284,"uid":311128,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2